title: Looking for a 3V3 Partner
body:
Looking for a 3V3 Ranked Partner, no Discord/ Teamspeak needed.

U like to play 3v3 and you're a motivated ad/ap player? 
Simply add me and write you preferences, hopefully we can get along.
I'm a Renekton/ Malphite/Volibear player. I can play any position.

Greetings,  _Kronoses_.
